---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 233
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Death=Death Kills Death
  - 835
By: Chang Po-tuan
---
The white Tiger grows angry in the western mountains and the green
Dragon is irresistibly fierce in the eastern sea. Capture them with
both hands and let them fight to death. They then change into a layer
of the powder of purple gold.
